      <title outputclass="H4ForH3_1_9" class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">52.209-2</ph> Prohibition
on Contracting with Inverted Domestic Corporations-Representation.</title>
      <conbody outputclass="provision" class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p otherprops="Body"
            outputclass="Body"
            class="- topic/p "
            id="d3107e13">As
prescribed in <ph outputclass="ClauseProvisionXREF" class="- topic/ph ">
               <xref href="FAR-i1116431.dita#i1116431"
                     base="i1116431"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">9.108-5</xref>(a)</ph>, insert the following
provision:</p>
         <p otherprops="Ctr_SmCaps" outputclass="Ctr_SmCaps" class="- topic/p ">Prohibition on Contracting with Inverted
Domestic Corporations-Representation (Nov 2015)</p>
         <ol id="d3089e25" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d3107e29" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Definitions</i>.
“Inverted domestic corporation” and “subsidiary” have the meaning
given in the clause of this contract entitled Prohibition on Contracting
with Inverted Domestic Corporations (<xref href="FAR-i1062680.dita#i1062680"
                        base="i1062680"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.209-10</xref>).</p>
            </li>
            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d3107e44" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  Government agencies are not permitted
to use appropriated (or otherwise made available) funds for contracts
with either an inverted domestic corporation, or a subsidiary of
an inverted domestic corporation, unless the exception at <xref href="FAR-i1116407.dita#i1116407"
                        base="i1116407"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">9.108-2</xref>(b)
applies or the requirement is waived in accordance with the procedures
at <xref href="FAR-i1116422.dita#i1116422"
                        base="i1116422"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">9.108-4</xref>.</p>
            </li>
            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d3107e59" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Representation</i>.
The Offeror represents that-</p>
               <ol id="d3089e68" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li otherprops="123" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d3107e72" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        It □is, □is not an inverted domestic
corporation; and</p>
                  </li>
                  <li otherprops="123" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d3107e81" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        It □is, □is not a subsidiary of
an inverted domestic corporation.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
         </ol>
         <p otherprops="Body_Endofprovision" class="- topic/p ">(End
of provision)</p>
